201cAnd if he returns?\u201d The student said, \u201cI will fight him!\u201d The elder said, \u201cAnd if he returns?\u201d The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13007,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/20\/shaytan-al-waswas-al-khannas\/","url_meta":{"origin":38593,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Shaytan: Devil waiting for man to forget Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Satan is lying in wait over the heart of the son of Adam. If he remembers Allah, Satan retreats. If he forgets Allah, Satan will devour his heart; that is the 'whisperer who retreats.'\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23916,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/10\/26\/fudayl-forgive-defeat-shaytan\/","url_meta":{"origin":38593,"position":3},"title":"Fudayl on Mercy: Whoever forgives others has defeated Satan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 26, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Razin reported: A man came to Al-Fudayl ibn Bazwan, may Allah have mercy on him, and he said, \u201cIndeed, a man has slandered you!\u201d Al-Fudayl said, \u201cVerily, I will infuriate the one who commanded him! May Allah forgive me and forgive him.\u201d It was said, \u201cWho has commanded him?\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38878,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/22\/yad-allah-jamaah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38593,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jama\u2019ah: Hand of Allah above united Muslim community","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 22, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Arfajah ibn Shurayh reported: I saw the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, delivering a sermon to the people, saying, \u201cVerily, the Hand of Allah is over the united community, for Satan is with one who secedes from the community, running after him.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 4020 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9922,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/24\/prophet-serves-himself\/","url_meta":{"origin":38593,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Chores: The Prophet humblys serve himself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I was asked, \u201cWhat did the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, do\u00a0in his home?\u201d I said, \u201cThe Prophet\u00a0was a man among men. He would remove fleas from his clothes, milk his sheep, and serve himself.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 26194 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/38593","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=38593"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/38593\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=38593"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=38593"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=38593"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}